query: SELECT SUM(Project_ID), Document_Name FROM Documents_with_Expenses JOIN Documents ON Documents_with_Expenses.Document_ID = Documents.Document_ID WHERE  Documents_with_Expenses.Document_ID >= 8 AND Document_Date IN (SELECT Document_Date FROM Documents AS r WHERE r.Project_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10) ORDER BY Document_Name DESC
SELECT m.Project_ID FROM Projects AS m JOIN Projects ON Projects.Project_ID = m.Project_ID WHERE  m.Project_ID <= 84

SELECT Documents.Document_ID, Document_Type_Code FROM Documents_with_Expenses JOIN Documents JOIN Projects ON Documents.Project_ID = Projects.Project_ID AND Documents_with_Expenses.Document_ID = Documents.Document_ID GROUP BY Document_Type_Code
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Document_Date), Document_Type_Code FROM Documents WHERE  Project_ID > 99 GROUP BY Document_Type_Code ORDER BY Document_Type_Code ASC

SELECT Accounts.Statement_ID, Document_Name FROM Documents JOIN Statements JOIN Accounts ON Documents.Document_ID = Statements.Statement_ID AND Statements.Statement_ID = Accounts.Statement_ID WHERE  Statements.Statement_ID < 25 ORDER BY Document_Name DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT Projects.Project_ID, Document_Type_Code FROM Documents JOIN Projects ON Documents.Project_ID = Projects.Project_ID WHERE  Documents.Project_ID != 23 GROUP BY Document_Type_Code

SELECT v.Document_Description, v.Other_Details FROM Documents JOIN Documents AS v ON Documents.Document_ID = v.Document_ID WHERE  v.Project_ID = 98 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Projects AS c WHERE  c.Project_ID > 59 AND Documents.Document_ID = c.Project_ID LIMIT 2)
SELECT Project_ID, Project_Details FROM Projects WHERE Project_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY Project_Details HAVING AVG(Project_ID) = 13
SELECT MAX(Document_ID), Document_Description FROM Documents WHERE Document_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  Project_ID < 32 GROUP BY Document_Description HAVING MIN(Document_ID) < 97 LIMIT 10

SELECT AVG(Documents.Document_ID), Document_Description FROM Documents_with_Expenses JOIN Documents JOIN Projects ON Documents.Project_ID = Projects.Project_ID AND Documents_with_Expenses.Document_ID = Documents.Document_ID WHERE  Documents.Document_ID > 28

SELECT AVG(Documents.Project_ID), Other_Details, Document_Description FROM Documents JOIN Projects JOIN Statements JOIN Accounts ON Documents.Project_ID = Projects.Project_ID AND Documents.Document_ID = Statements.Statement_ID AND Statements.Statement_ID = Accounts.Statement_ID WHERE  Account_ID > 40 GROUP BY Document_Description HAVING SUM(Accounts.Statement_ID) <= 55 ORDER BY Other_Details ASC LIMIT 8

SELECT MAX(Project_ID), Statement_Details, Document_Name FROM Documents_with_Expenses JOIN Documents JOIN Ref_Budget_Codes JOIN Statements ON Documents.Document_ID = Statements.Statement_ID AND Documents_with_Expenses.Document_ID = Documents.Document_ID AND Ref_Budget_Codes.Budget_Type_Code = Documents_with_Expenses.Budget_Type_Code WHERE  Project_ID >= 65 GROUP BY Document_Name HAVING SUM(Project_ID) >= 22 LIMIT 9
SELECT COUNT(Account_ID) FROM Accounts WHERE Statement_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 LIMIT 9

SELECT u.Budget_Type_Code, u.Document_Details FROM Documents_with_Expenses AS u WHERE u.Document_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Document_ID != (SELECT MAX(Document_ID) FROM Documents WHERE Project_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  Document_ID > 11 LIMIT 5) GROUP BY u.Document_Details HAVING SUM(u.Document_ID) < 55

SELECT Other_Details, Document_Name, Document_Type_Code FROM Documents WHERE Project_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Document_Type_Code IN (SELECT Document_Type_Code FROM Documents AS n WHERE n.Document_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10) GROUP BY Document_Type_Code

SELECT AVG(Accounts.Statement_ID), COUNT(Statements.Statement_ID) FROM Statements JOIN Accounts ON Statements.Statement_ID = Accounts.Statement_ID WHERE Accounts.Statement_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Statements AS r WHERE r.Statement_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Accounts.Account_ID = r.Statement_ID)
SELECT Document_ID, Document_ID FROM Documents_with_Expenses WHERE Document_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 ORDER BY Document_ID DESC LIMIT 2
SELECT MIN(Project_ID), Project_Details FROM Projects WHERE  Project_ID > 26 ORDER BY Project_Details DESC

SELECT AVG(Document_ID), Document_Type_Name FROM Ref_Document_Types JOIN Documents JOIN Statements ON Documents.Document_ID = Statements.Statement_ID AND Ref_Document_Types.Document_Type_Code = Documents.Document_Type_Code WHERE Statement_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  Project_ID = 52
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT j.Document_ID), j.Budget_Type_Code, j.Document_Details FROM Documents_with_Expenses AS j WHERE  j.Document_ID > 29 GROUP BY j.Document_Details
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT f.Project_Details), f.Project_ID, f.Project_Details FROM Projects AS f WHERE  f.Project_ID < 67 GROUP BY f.Project_Details

SELECT Documents.Document_ID, w.Other_Details, w.Document_Name FROM Documents JOIN Documents AS w ON Documents.Document_ID = w.Document_ID WHERE w.Project_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  Documents.Project_ID >= 97 GROUP BY w.Document_Name LIMIT 9
SELECT a.Document_ID, a.Document_Date FROM Documents AS a WHERE Project_ID IN (SELECT Project_ID FROM Projects) GROUP BY a.Document_Date

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Document_Type_Code), Documents_with_Expenses.Document_ID, Project_ID, Document_Details FROM Documents_with_Expenses JOIN Documents ON Documents_with_Expenses.Document_ID = Documents.Document_ID WHERE Documents.Document_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Statements WHERE  Statement_ID != 11 AND Documents.Document_ID = Statement_ID) GROUP BY Document_Details

SELECT MAX(Documents_with_Expenses.Document_ID), COUNT(DISTINCT Document_Description), Documents.Document_ID FROM Documents_with_Expenses JOIN Documents JOIN Ref_Budget_Codes JOIN Ref_Document_Types ON Documents_with_Expenses.Document_ID = Documents.Document_ID AND Ref_Document_Types.Document_Type_Code = Documents.Document_Type_Code AND Ref_Budget_Codes.Budget_Type_Code = Documents_with_Expenses.Budget_Type_Code WHERE Document_Name NOT IN (SELECT Document_Name FROM Documents WHERE Document_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10)
